Eight people have been confirmed dead in the southern state of Northern Bahr el Ghazal, Sudan. (Sudan Tribune) (africannewslive)12 people die and 7 others receive wounds during a torch attack in Rawalpindi, Pakistan, on a convoy of more than a dozen oil tankers intended for NATO forces in Afghanistan. This follows a dispute over a NATO helicopter strike that killed 3 soldiers in Pakistan territory. (AFP via The Age) (The New York Times), (BBC)